## Owner debug logs (list / details)

Per **`angular-project`** — in every donation list or details **`subscribe` `next`**, log the parsed response so the owner can confirm **`response.message`** shape matches the doc:

```ts
console.log('listPendingReviewRequests response', response);
console.log('listEntityDonationRequests response', response);
console.log('getDonationRequestDetails response', results);
console.log('statuses response', response);
```

Do **not** remove these when editing the same file unless the owner asks.
